 Test and Correct Data in the ENDF FORMAT (FIXUP 2023-1)
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Interpretation of Input Test/Correction Options
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Correct ZA/AWR in All Sections----------  Yes (Required for ALL ENDF Data)
 Correct Thresholds----------------------   No (No Longer Allowed)
 Extend Cross Section to 20 MeV----------   No (No Longer Allowed)
 Allow Cross Section Deletion------------   No                     
 Allow Cross Section Reconstruction------  Yes (Use Built-in Table)
 Make All Cross Sections Non-Negative----  Yes
 Delete Energies Not in Ascending Order--  Yes
 Delete Duplicate Points-----------------  Yes
 Check for Ascending MAT/MF/MT Order-----  Yes
 Check for Legal MF/MT Numbers-----------  Yes
 Allow Creation of Missing Sections------   No
 Allow Insertion of Energy Points--------   No
 Uniform Energy Grid for ALL MT----------   No
 Delete Section if Cross Section =0------  Yes
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 ENDF Input and Output Data FilenameS
 LINEAR.OUT                                                              
 FIXUP.OUT                                                               
